Berkshire Hathaway HomeServices Starck Real Estate

data.description: Highly Custom Built in 2002 Br/Hardy Board Ranch style home nestled away from the street in the desirable Shade Tree Cir community. Featuring a long private driveway for additional cars, large wrap around porch, rear deck and a 3C-Attached Garage. Interior features ample space and an open floor plan design. Custom kitchen with large island with granite countertops, custom built cabinetry and high end SS Appliances, which opens to the living room with Fireplace and dining area. Hardwood floors  and volume ceilings are featured on the main floor. Large Primary bedroom with full bath and walk in closet. Property has 3 bedrooms and Den can be converted into 4th bedroom.  Huge Finished basement with full bath. additional fireplace, media area and storage room. This is a must see home with many possibilities!
